  "task": "Replace the contents of /home/user/godot_projects/shader_game/scripts/grayscale.gdshader with a valid Godot 4 canvas_item shader that samples the input texture at UV and converts the color to grayscale using luminance weights (0.299, 0.587, 0.114).\n\nThe shader must include all of these exactly:\n\nshader_type canvas_item;\n\nvoid fragment() {\n\tvec4 c = texture(TEXTURE, UV);\n\tfloat gray = c.r * 0.299 + c.g * 0.587 + c.b * 0.114;\n\tCOLOR = vec4(gray, gray, gray, c.a);\n}\n\nSave the file.",
